{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A Good Field &quot;is a strategy simulation and construction game with rich gameplay, which combines various gameplay such as strategy battles, city construction, and leisure competitions. Multiple national camps are waiting for you to join, freely develop and build your city, and fight in all directions at any time. As the decision maker of the empire, you lead your subjects in the footsteps of faith to achieve immortal dominance.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Firstly, the game has a level based gameplay, where players need to start from level 1 and complete tasks before advancing to the next level, until reaching full level.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Secondly, there is</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Construction, players can choose to build buildings that have already been developed and constructed, and the construction conditions may require the consumption of some resources to build.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In agriculture, players can cultivate rice, wheat, flax, mulberry leaves, tree paint, and other crops to obtain food and raw materials.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Industry, players can build industrial buildings, which can produce daily necessities such as porcelain, lacquerware, copperware, textiles, paper, jade, etc.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Military, players can train soldiers of various branches of the army, plunder player resources, and attack other cities on the world map through gameplay.</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3342270/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1733843500","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3342270/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1733843500","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3342270/f4bb1802944b7cb3b406990e1d5c26279b17771a/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1733843500","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3342270/f4bb1802944b7cb3b406990e1d5c26279b17771a/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1733843500","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"In-App Purchases","id":35}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A Good Field &quot;is a strategy simulation and construction game with rich gameplay, which combines various gameplay such as strategy battles, city construction, and leisure competitions. Multiple national camps are waiting for you to join, freely develop and build your city, and fight in all directions at any time. As the decision maker of the empire, you lead your subjects in the footsteps of faith to achieve immortal dominance.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Firstly, the game has a level based gameplay, where players need to start from level 1 and complete tasks before advancing to the next level, until reaching full level.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Secondly, there is</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Construction, players can choose to build buildings that have already been developed and constructed, and the construction conditions may require the consumption of some resources to build.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In agriculture, players can cultivate rice, wheat, flax, mulberry leaves, tree paint, and other crops to obtain food and raw materials.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Industry, players can build industrial buildings, which can produce daily necessities such as porcelain, lacquerware, copperware, textiles, paper, jade, etc.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Military, players can train soldiers of various branches of the army, plunder player resources, and attack other cities on the world map through gameplay.</p>","developers":["\u6b66\u5668\u94fa\u5de5\u4f5c\u5ba4"],"genres":[{"description":"Casual","id":"4"},{"description":"Indie","id":"23"},{"description":"Massively Multiplayer","id":"29"},{"description":"RPG","id":"3"},{"description":"Simulation","id":"2